         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633"><!-- p4l4-r17 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-Hd1e108">Rubrica 17</head> 
            <!-- this doesn't seem to be in Chris's list -->
    <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-Hd1e113" type="question-title">De conuiuiis.</head>
    <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-d1e116">
               <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>
      ¶ De conuiuiis. ¶ Rubrica. 17
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="49"/> <ref>IEsus filius sirach in eccle
      <lb ed="#V" n="50" break="no"/>siast. c. 30.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-Qd1e127">Spledidu:
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>cor bonum in epulis: epule enim il
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>lius diligentes fiunt.</quote>
               <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>qu <!-- line coord error ? -->
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-d1e140">
               <lb ed="#V" n="54"/> <ref>Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum: lib. 3. c. 5</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-Qd1e146">Ante circumspiciendum est cum quibus edas
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>et bibas: quam quid edas et bibas. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-d1e152">
               <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>
          <ref>¶ Ualerius maximus. l. 2 ti. de institutis an
        <lb ed="#V" n="58" break="no"/>tiquis:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-Qd1e156">Conuiuium solenne maiores institue
        <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>runt: idque charistiam appellauerunt: cui pre
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>ter cognatos et affines nemo interponebatur
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>vt siqua inter necessarias personas quere
        <lb ed="#V" n="62" break="no"/>la esset orta apud sacra mense et inter hylarim
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>tatem animorum a fautoribus concordie
        <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>tolleretur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-d1e175">
               <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>
       <ref>¶ Macrobius satumaliorum: li. 3. in pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="66" break="no"/>hemio</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-Qd1e179">Solet cibus cum sumitur tacitos essi
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>cere: potus loquaces.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-d1e187">
               <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>
       <ref>¶ Cato capistolo. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-Qd1e191">Conuiuare raro.
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>Pauca in conuiuio loquere. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-d1e197"> 
       <ref>/ Capistolo. 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-Qd1e199">Dapsilis interdum notis et caris amicis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-d1e205">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
       <ref>/ Capitulo. 4.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-Qd1e209">Inter conuiuas fac sis sermone modestus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>Ne dicare loquax dum vis vrbanus heberi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-d1e218">
               <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>
       <ref>¶ Uersificator fabularium esopi. 22. f.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d86633-Qd1e222">In te
        <lb ed="#V" n="75" break="no"/>nui mensa satis est immensa voluptas.
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>Nobilitat namque frons generosa dapes.
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>Emendet conditque cibos clementia vultus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>Conuiuam saciat plus dape frontis honor.
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>Tristitior immensas pauperat vsus opes.</quote>
            </p>
